BACKGROUND GENSYMCID-1875, "write regression test for GENSYMCID-686", where 686 is entitled "Error with G2 utility KB GXL procedure: gxl-set-color-pattern-of-cell-to-default". Under some circumstances, calling the procedure caused an error at G2 2011 December edition, see GENSYMCID-686 for further details.
SOLUTION We had to reproduce test scenario, catch the error and analyze the error message to find out is it a regression or another kind of problem.
TESTING Test fails at G2 2011 Std December release and passes at our delivery branch forked from integrate/HIP2016-08.
NOTES We use player.kb to have an access to procedure returning G2 server window.
